Dynamically serve search-optimized local landing pages generated by LocalLeads under your WordPress site's domain.

== Description ==

LocalLeads automatically builds search-optimized landing pages for every town and service your business covers. This plugin lets you seamlessly host those pages on your WordPress website without writing any code or uploading raw files.

== Installation ==

1. Upload the entire `localleads-seo` folder to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory, or upload the ZIP file directly via the WordPress admin panel (Plugins > Add New > Upload Plugin).
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress.
3. Go to Settings > LocalLeads SEO to configure your Client ID and URL prefix.
4. Save settings. If you change the URL Prefix, visit the Settings > Permalinks page once to flush the rewrite rules.
